<F P=106> [TA SR report: "Checking on Quality"] </F>
  [Text] Bratislava--Ivan Gasparovic, chairman of the 
National Council of the Slovak Republic, presented letters of 
appointment to new members of the Slovak Television Council in 
Bratislava yesterday. On this occasion, he mentioned their 
responsibility under the law to check on the quality of 
