Council. Jozef Prusak told TA SR that the reconstructed 
council, whose other two members are Eva Kristinova and Dusan 
Jariabek, wants to become thoroughly conversant with materials 
being prepared for the parliament, as well as with documents 
pertaining to the operation of Slovak Television. This applies, 
in particular, to the television statutes and to the code of 
ethics of employees of this public corporation that is to be 
drafted. 

