  [Text] Sarajevo, May 17 (TANJUG) -- The Moslem forces on 
Tuesday [17 May] launched mortar and anti-aircraft attacks on 
Serb positions and settlements in the Sarajevo front, Bosnian 
Serb military sources have said. The sources said that in the 
Ilijas area the Moslems fired 82mm mortars on Serb positions, 
and opened anti-aircraft fire on the Krcevine region from the 
Visocica area. In the Ilidza part of the Sarajevo front, the 
