settlement and Serb positions in the area of the forestry school 
and the Vrucci suburb. Moslem snipers on Tuesday opened fire 
from the direction of the Vojnicko Polje on Nedjarici, from the 
direction of Strupsko Brdo on Kasindolska street, from the right 
bank of the Miljacka river on Grbavica, and from the direction 
of Sokolje on the Rajlovac barracks, the Bosnian Serb Army 
sources said. 

