<F P=100> BULGARIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Zhelev To Hold Talks With SDS Leader </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Zhelev To Hold Talks With SDS Leader </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2005103894 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1000 
GMT 20 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2005103894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Today the chairman of the parliamentary group of 
the SDS [Union of Democratic Forces] accepted an invitation from 
President Zhelyu Zhelev to meet for talks to discuss the signing 
of a parliamentary agreement on passing certain high-priority 
laws, forming a caretaker cabinet, and setting a date for 
parliamentary elections. The president is expected to make a 
public statement on this matter later. 

</TEXT>

