headed by Vice Prime Minister Perica Jukic, was last night 
harassed and threatened at gunpoint between Gornji Vakuf and 
Novi Travnik, an area under the control of the armed forces of 
Bosnia-Herzegovina. Another official HVO delegation was stopped 
and mistreated in the same area yesterday. 

